This script assumes you are installing the Haxiot Gateway on a Linux system. It has been tested on Raspian and Ubuntu, but will likely work on others as this it is build from source. If you would like to run this on Mac or Windows, please download the Haxiot vGateway virtual machine w/ TheThingsNetwork setup from {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.haxiot.com/support"}}{\fldrslt www.haxiot.com/support}}\
